   <div class="column left">
      <h2>Introducing qTip.</h2>
      <p>qTip is an advanced tooltip plugin for the ever popular <a href="http://jquery.com">jQuery JavaScript framework</a>.</p>

      <p>Built from the ground up to be <b>user friendly</b>, yet <a href="/projects/qtip/features">feature rich</a>, qTip provides you with tonnes of features like <b>rounded corners</b> and <b>speech bubble tips</b>, and best of all... it's <a href="/projects/qtip/download#license">completely free under the MIT license!</a></p>

   </div>

